{"id": "art-152", "label": "Art. 152", "title": "Art. 152", "slug": "art-152", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 152 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1729631312\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2153\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1729631312\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Directorii sunt r&#259;spunz&#259;tori pentru\nneîndeplinirea îndatoririlor lor. Prevederile art. 137<sup>1</sup> alin. (3),\nale art. 144<sup>1</sup>, 144<sup>3</sup>, 144<sup>4</sup>, </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>150</span><span style='color:black'> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nale art. 153<sup>12</sup> alin. (4) se aplic&#259; directorilor în <span\nclass=SpellE>acelea&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ii</span> ca <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> administratorilor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1300843229\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2152\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1300843229\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Remunera&#355;ia</span> directorilor,\n<span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inut&#259;</span> în temeiul contractului de mandat,\neste asimilat&#259; din punct de vedere fiscal veniturilor din salarii <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> se impoziteaz&#259; potrivit <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;iei</span>\nîn materie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1403264489\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2151\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1403264489\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Prin derogare de la art. 5 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>19/2000</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind sistemul public de pensii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nalte drepturi de asigur&#259;ri sociale, cu modific&#259;rile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile ulterioare, <span class=SpellE>remunera&#355;ia</span>\ndirectorilor <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inut&#259;</span> în temeiul\ncontractului de mandat este asimilat&#259; salariului, din punctul de vedere al\n<span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span> decurgând pentru director <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> societate din <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span>\nprivind sistemul public de pensii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> alte\ndrepturi de asigur&#259;ri sociale, inclusiv dreptul de asigurare pentru\naccidente de munc&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> boli profesionale, <span\nclass=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span> privind sistemul asigur&#259;rilor pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;omaj</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> stimularea\nocup&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>for&#355;ei</span> de munc&#259;, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> din <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span>\nprivind asigur&#259;rile de s&#259;n&#259;tate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}